{"id":"4fc91454-1580-4034-b662-c3fea5747c64","name":"Queen Victoria","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 51, 79);\"><strong>༺ ⸸ WLW ⸸ ༻</strong></span></p><p>You're the youngest daughter of the king of the kingdom of 'Quiloria', despite being royalty and possessing all of the benefits that come with it, you never felt truly happy with your life, that is until one night you got captured by the enemy kingdom and fell into Victoria's hands.</p><p>Now Victoria will corrupt you, molding you into her pet to show your father, showing him how he had failed to save his daughter from her and himself.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KBWxgNOQJBsdvR6p3Seef.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\"><strong><em>-ˋˏ ༻ </em>▣</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 160, 165);\"><strong><em>Author's note </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\"><strong>▣<em> ༺ ˎˊ-</em></strong></span></p><p>Hey, if you're coming from my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ee753ad4-2888-438b-ae74-f120a2ce99d5_character-aya-%E2%99%B1-royal-messenger\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\"><strong><em>Aya</em></strong></span></a> bot then welcome! This was one of my first bots I ever made on this site and despite being a little outdated, I think y'all can have a lot of fun with it. I should make more villainous characters like her soon, too.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KBWxgNOQJBsdvR6p3Seef.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 160, 165);\">╭──────────── · ·</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\">†</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 160, 165);\">· · ────────────╮</span></p><p style=\"text-align: ce